<% content_for(:title, "About Us - Crewbnb") %>
<% meta_description "Crewbnb was built by hosts who house contractors. We created a booking site for worker accommodation because nothing else was built for this." %>

<%# ===== HERO ===== %>
<section class="bg-[#0F224F] pt-10 pb-16">
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6">
    <p class="text-blue-200/60 text-sm font-medium mb-2">About Crewbnb</p>
    <h1 class="font-headline text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white leading-[1.1] tracking-tight mb-4 max-w-2xl">
      We built this because nothing else was built for workers.
    </h1>
    <p class="text-blue-200/80 text-base md:text-lg max-w-lg">
      Crewbnb started with one problem: contractors need beds near job sites, not holiday lets at tourist prices.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<%# ===== OUR STORY ===== %>
<section class="bg-white py-16">
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-slate-100 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600 mb-8">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base">location_on</span>
        Made in Tulfarris, Wicklow
      </div>

      <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Our story</h2>

      <div class="space-y-5 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          We started as hosts ourselves. We had properties sitting empty Monday to Friday while workers drove hours to job sites and overpaid for weekend-priced Airbnbs that weren't set up for them.
        </p>
        <p>
          The workers needed beds, parking, fast WiFi, and a proper invoice for their accountant. What they got was tourist apartments with hot tubs, no parking, and a checkout process designed for holidaymakers.
        </p>
        <p>
          So we built Crewbnb. A booking site for worker accommodation. Weekday pricing. Automatic invoices. Properties set up for people who wake up at 6am and need somewhere to sleep near site.
        </p>
        <p>
          No frills. No tourist markup. Just practical stays for working people.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# ===== WHAT WE BELIEVE ===== %>
<section class="bg-slate-50 py-16 border-t border-slate-100">
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6">
    <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 text-center mb-12">What we believe</h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-[#0F224F] flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-xl">payments</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Fair pricing</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Workers shouldn't pay weekend rates for weekday stays. Our hosts set prices that make sense for the work week.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-[#0F224F] flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-xl">receipt_long</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">No admin hassle</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Every booking generates a proper invoice automatically. No chasing receipts, no manual paperwork.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-[#0F224F] flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-xl">engineering</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-headline font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Built for workers</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Beds, parking, laundry, fast WiFi. Properties listed here are set up for people who work, not holiday.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# ===== BY THE NUMBERS ===== %>
<section class="bg-white py-16 border-t border-slate-100">
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6">
    <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 text-center mb-12">Crewbnb at a glance</h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div>
        <p class="font-headline text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#0F224F]">8</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">Cities</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-headline text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#0F224F]">20+</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">Properties</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-headline text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#0F224F]">15-25%</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">Avg. savings</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-headline text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#0F224F]">2 min</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">To book</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# ===== CTA ===== %>
<section class="bg-slate-50 py-16 border-t border-slate-100">
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="bg-[#0F224F] rounded-2xl px-8 py-14 md:px-16 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-3">
        Ready to try it?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-blue-200/60 max-w-md mx-auto mb-8 text-sm">
        Find accommodation near your next job site. Or list your property and start earning from empty weekdays.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <%= link_to properties_path, class: "bg-white text-[#0F224F] px-7 py-3 rounded-xl font-semibold text-sm hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors" do %>
          Find a stay
        <% end %>
        <%= link_to new_user_registration_path(role: "host"), class: "border border-white/25 text-white px-7 py-3 rounded-xl font-semibold text-sm hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors" do %>
          List your property
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
